(FM.SHADE  [LAMBDA (X SHADE WINDOW)                               (* jow "26-Jun-86 14:59")         (* X is a group id or an item. Paint shade on top of group or item.)    (\FM.INSUREWINDOW WINDOW)    (LET [(REGION (OR (\FM.GROUPPROP WINDOW X 'REGION)                      (\FM.ITEMPROP (\FM.INSUREFM X WINDOW)                             'REGION]         (if (AND REGION (OPENWP WINDOW))             then (BLTSHADE (TEXTUREP SHADE)                             WINDOW NIL NIL NIL NIL 'PAINT REGION])

